When has SOE or Verant EVER said that we are the masters of pet heals? Or even that we <span style="font-style: italic">should</span> be the masters of pet heals?
<br />

<br />
Why doesn't my plan work? This way, Magicians and Beastlords both get adequate pet heals, but the Beastlord one is more efficient.  Why doesn't that work?  If you say "well it makes more sense to just throw more elemental 'stuff' into the mix," then you're just being envious and close-minded.  Give me a better reason than that roleplay "well it would make more sense if you did it this way" bullshit.  As far as I'm concerned, there is nothing that you have said so far that will convince SOE to make Magicians better than Beastlords at healing their pets.  So until then...
<br />

<br />
